OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FThe Children's Commissioner for
OL,7,FEngland Dame Rachel de Souza discussed
OL,8,Fher concerns with ITV News Social
OL,9,FAffairs Correspondent Sarah Corker
OL,11,FCouncils don't have enough funding or
OL,12,Fstaff to carry out tough new duties
OL,13,Faround home education, the Children's
OL,14,FCommissioner for England has warned.
OL,16,FDame Rachel de Souza told ITV News
OL,17,Fthat there is a "real difference of
OL,18,Fpractice across the country" regarding
OL,19,Fthe oversight of children who are
OL,20,Ftaught at home and warned that council
OL,21,Fstaff already have "massive caseloads".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FThe Children's Wellbeing and Schools
OL,7,FBill will create a register of all
OL,8,Fhome-educated children, and councils
OL,9,Fwill have to check family homes are
OL,10,F"suitable learning environments".
OL,12,FIn some circumstances, parents will
OL,13,Fhave to get permission from the local
OL,14,Fauthority to withdraw their children
OL,15,Ffrom school, such as those on child
OL,16,Fprotection plans.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FMinisters say the bill will help
OL,7,Fprotect vulnerable children and
OL,8,Fprevent future cases like that of
OL,9,Fmurdered ten-year-old Sara Sharif, who
OL,10,Fwas killed by her father and
OL,11,Fstepmother after they removed her from
OL,12,Fschool.
OL,14,FThe Children's Commissioner supports
OL,15,Fthe tighter regulation but warns that
OL,16,Fwithout adequate funding to back up
OL,17,Fthe new measures, it will be difficult
OL,18,Fto ensure "a consistent, high quality
OL,19,Fservice" across all councils.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FDame Rachel de Souza, the Children's
OL,7,FCommissioner for England, told ITV
OL,8,FNews 'schools are for everyone'
OL,10,FHeather Sandy, from the Association of
OL,11,FDirectors of Children's Services,
OL,12,Fwhich has long called for a national
OL,13,Fhome education register, warned that
OL,14,F"local authorities need powers to
OL,15,Fmatch current and new responsibilities
OL,16,Fto assure themselves that children are
OL,17,Fsafe and receiving a good education".
OL,19,F"It is crucial this is met with the
OL,20,Ffunding to allow us to carry out our
OL,21,Fstatutory duties well," she added.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
