OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FThe number of children being home
OL,7,Feducated in England has continued to
OL,8,Frise steadily since the pandemic,
OL,9,Faccording to Department for Education
OL,10,Ffigures.
OL,12,FThere were 126,000 children in
OL,13,Felective home education in England in
OL,14,Fautumn 2025, up from 111,700 in the
OL,15,Fprevious year and 92,000 in 2023,
OL,16,Fwhich marks a 37% increase.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
