CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FExperts say the trend is being driven
OL,7,Fby parents who are concerned about
OL,8,Ftheir children's mental health or
OL,9,Finadequate support for those with
OL,10,Fspecial education needs and
OL,11,Fdisabilities (SEND).
OL,13,FKatrina Farrell, who home educates her
OL,14,Fteenage daughter Alice, told ITV News
OL,15,Fthat withdrawing her from school was
OL,16,Fthe most 'difficult decision I've ever
OL,17,Fhad to make'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FKatrina Farrell, who home educates her
OL,7,Fteenage daughter in Knaresborough,
OL,8,Fnorth Yorkshire, described withdrawing
OL,9,Fher from school as the most "difficult
OL,10,Fdecision I've ever had to make".
OL,12,F"I watched a nine-year-old girl go
OL,13,Finto a mental health crisis, and
OL,14,Fthat's where we were," she told ITV
OL,15,FNews.
OL,17,F"She wasn't eating, she wasn't
OL,18,Ftalking. It was really obvious that it
OL,19,Fwas serious, and you've got to do
OL,20,Fsomething."
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FAlice, who is autistic, felt
OL,7,Funsupported at primary school and
OL,8,Fdescribed being in "survival mode".
OL,9,FHer anxiety became so great that she
OL,10,Fstruggled to talk, eat or leave the
OL,11,Fhouse at times.
OL,13,FSeven years on, aged 15, Alice is
OL,14,Fthriving.
OL,16,FHaving already taken her GCSEs and A
OL,17,FLevels, she is now studying at the
OL,18,FOpen University with ambitions to
OL,19,Fbecome a speech and language therapist.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FWhile she accepts that home education
OL,7,Fis not for everyone, she told ITV News
OL,8,Fthat she believes the mainstream
OL,9,Fschool system is failing too many
OL,10,Fchildren and described it as a "toxic
OL,11,Fenvironment".
OL,13,FAlice, who is 15, told ITV News she
OL,14,Ffelt unsupported in school and
OL,15,Fdescribed being in 'survival mode',
OL,16,Fbut is now thriving after seven years
OL,17,Fof home education
OL,19,FHer mother described the new rules
OL,20,Faround home education as "intrusive".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,F"There is no more risk educating at
OL,7,Fhome than there is at school," Ms
OL,8,FFarrell told ITV News. "Our
OL,9,Fsafeguarding laws and policies work in
OL,10,Fexactly the same way.
OL,12,F"If you want to hide a child, you can
OL,13,Fdo that whilst they're at school. Just
OL,14,Fas easily as you could if they were
OL,15,Fhome educated."
OL,17,FIn the UK, anyone can home educate
OL,18,Ftheir kids. There are a few checks,
OL,19,Fand children don't have to do exams or
OL,20,Ffollow the curriculum.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FEven with the new legislation, Britain
OL,7,Fhas some of the most lax rules in
OL,8,FEurope on this issue.
OL,10,FSir David Holmes, the Chair of the
OL,11,FChild Safeguarding Practice Review
OL,12,FPanel, said that while the majority of
OL,13,Fparents do a good job, experts are
OL,14,Fworried about the most vulnerable
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,F"The risk is that a child who is home
OL,18,Feducated becomes invisible," he told
OL,19,FITV News. "They lose the protective
OL,20,Ffactor of being at school.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,F"They lose the protective factor of
OL,7,Fsort of being exposed to people and
OL,8,Fnetworks outside the home who might be
OL,9,Fable to support them if something's
OL,10,Fgoing wrong. That's the challenge, how
OL,11,Fto keep those children safe."
OL,13,FSir David Holmes, the Chair of the
OL,14,FChild Safeguarding Practice Review
OL,15,FPanel, told ITV News that while the
OL,16,Fmajority of parents do a good job,
OL,17,Fthere are concerns for the most
OL,18,Fvulnerable children
OL,26,@sD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FThe scale and concentration of
OL,7,Fchildren being deregistered is
OL,8,Fworrying experts, who described
OL,9,Fschools as a crucial part of the
OL,10,Fsocial safety net.
OL,12,FThere are also questions over whether
OL,13,Fcouncils have the expertise and
OL,14,Fresources to take on these new duties.
OL,16,FAmanda Jackson, an independent social
OL,17,Fworker for 37 years, warned that "we
OL,18,Frisk more and more children becoming
OL,19,Flost in a system".
OL,26,@yD@bOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,F"At the moment, there is virtually no
OL,7,Foversight of home educated children,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,FResearch by the NSPCC has found that
OL,11,Fhome education officers in local
OL,12,Fauthorities are responsible for an
OL,13,Faverage of 388 children each.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, some councils have no
OL,15,Fdedicated officers.
OL,17,F"Everybody's currently under so much
OL,18,Fpressure. I don't see with the current
OL,19,Fsystem how they could extend that out
OL,20,Fto support people that were home
OL,21,Fschooling."
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FMs Jackson, who is the British
OL,7,FAssociation of Social Workers' (BASW)
OL,8,Fsocial work expert, said there needs
OL,9,Fto be a complete reset of the system.
OL,11,F"I think it did need to be a
OL,12,Fcompletely separate body that draws on
OL,13,Fthe skills of social workers and
OL,14,Feducationalists, and that their sole
OL,15,Fpurpose is to protect the needs of
OL,16,Fchildren that are home schooled," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FAmanda Jackson, an independent social
OL,7,Fworker for 37 years, warned there is a
OL,8,Frisk of 'more and more children
OL,9,Fbecoming lost in a system'
OL,11,FITV News analysis shows some of the
OL,12,Fsteepest increases in kids being home
OL,13,Feducated are in areas with high levels
OL,14,Fof deprivation, raising concerns about
OL,15,Fa widening disadvantage gap.
OL,17,FIn Darlington, for example, one in 50
OL,18,Fchildren are home educated, while in
OL,19,FSunderland, the number of home
OL,20,Feducated children increased by 78% in
OL,21,Fone year alone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FEight-year-old Xanthe Fiskel from
OL,7,FSunderland has ADHD and is autistic.
OL,9,FHer parents, Natalie and Scott Fiskel,
OL,10,Fsaid a lack of support in the
OL,11,Fclassroom led them to withdraw her
OL,12,Ffrom school earlier this year.
OL,14,F"She was very upset and dysregulated
OL,15,Fand told me that she'd rather die than
OL,16,Fgo back to school, which obviously is
OL,17,Fquite upsetting, and it has to be
OL,18,Factioned," Xanthe's mother told ITV
OL,19,FNews.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,FSo far, Xanthe's parents have taken a
OL,7,Fsofter approach to learning, going at
OL,8,Fher own pace and focusing on subjects
OL,9,Fwhich she enjoys, including maths and
OL,10,Fart.
OL,12,FHowever, home educating is not
OL,13,Fsomething the family want to do long
OL,14,Fterm, instead describing it as a last
OL,15,Fresort.
OL,17,FThey've already had to cut back
OL,18,Ffinancially in order to pay for home
OL,19,Feducation resources.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,F"I don't think we've got any other
OL,7,Fchoice but to do it, but it is only in
OL,8,Fthe interim," she said. "We do want to
OL,9,Fget socialising with other children
OL,10,Fwho are like her."
OL,12,FFifteen miles away in North Tyneside,
OL,13,Fthe Tim Lamb Centre is helping more
OL,14,Fand more families who feel mainstream
OL,15,Fschool has failed their children. The
OL,16,Fdecision to home educate is often not
OL,17,Fa choice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/23
