CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775653863
OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,F"Over the past 18 months, we've seen a
OL,7,Fmassive increase in children being
OL,8,Fhome educated," said Joanna Handyside,
OL,9,FCEO at Pathways 4 All, which runs the
OL,10,Fcentre which supports children with
OL,11,FSEND.
OL,13,FJoanna Handyside, CEO at Pathways 4
OL,14,FAll, told ITV News they've seen a
OL,15,F'massive increase' in children being
OL,16,Fhome educated over the past 18 months
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/23
