OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,F"It's heartbreaking to talk to the
OL,7,Fparents, because they are at crisis
OL,8,Fand there's no worse thing than seeing
OL,9,Fyour child in pain but having to push
OL,10,Fyour child to go to school.
OL,12,F"They're often so upset, depressed,
OL,13,Fanxious and physically harm
OL,14,Fthemselves," she added.
OL,16,FA Department for Education
OL,17,Fspokesperson said, "In the vast
OL,18,Fmajority of cases, children achieve
OL,19,Fand thrive best in schools, although
OL,20,Fwe recognise that home education can
OL,21,Fbe the right choice for some families.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/23
