OL,3,CStricter home schooling rules prompt
OL,4,Cwarnings about overstretched councils
OL,6,F"Our reforms will help stop vulnerable
OL,7,Fchildren falling through the cracks
OL,8,Fand help councils take action to
OL,9,Fsupport children who are not receiving
OL,10,Fa suitable education, and we will give
OL,11,Fthem additional funding to do this."
OL,13,FIt added that the government is
OL,14,Fexpanding access to mental health
OL,15,Fsupport teams and "we are fixing the
OL,16,FSEND system so children get the right
OL,17,Fsupport earlier, without having to
OL,18,Ffight for it".
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@SOUzD@MO]
